OL,3,CFears for 300 jobs at BT call centre
OL,5,FThere are fears for around 300 jobs
OL,6,Fafter BT decided to close its call
OL,7,Fcentre in Enniskillen.
OL,9,FIt's understood the site provides
OL,10,Fsupport for EE mobile phone users.
OL,12,FEconomy Minister Deirdre Hargey
OL,13,Fdescribed the decision to withdraw the
OL,14,Fjobs by October as "extremely
OL,15,Fdisappointing".
OL,17,FShe said: "As a major employer in the
OL,18,Fregion for over three decades, this
OL,19,Fdecision is devastating for the
OL,20,Fworkers and their families, and also
OL,21,Ffor the wider community."
