OL,3,CFears for 300 jobs at BT call centre
OL,5,FFears for the jobs were first raised
OL,6,Fin February.
OL,8,FBT said it recently closed a
OL,9,F"generous" voluntary paid leavers
OL,10,Foffer which it said over 80% of
OL,11,Fcolleagues took up.
OL,13,FIt says it is proposing closing the
OL,14,Fsite to the remaining desk based staff
OL,15,Fon 31 October - and that it has
OL,16,Fentered into consultant with those
OL,17,Fstaff and unions.
OL,19,FBT said the Enniskillen centre
OL,20,Frequired significant improvements to
OL,21,Fmake it fit for purpose.
