OL,3,CFears for 300 jobs at BT call centre
OL,5,F"We have now made the difficult
OL,6,Fdecision to propose closing the site
OL,7,Fto the small number of remaining desk-
OL,8,Fbased colleagues on 31 October and
OL,9,Fhave entered into consultation with
OL,10,Fcolleagues and trade union partners,"
OL,11,Fthe spokesperson said.
OL,13,F"We will continue to support all
OL,14,Fimpacted colleagues throughout this
OL,15,Fprocess. These proposals will have no
OL,16,Fimpact for customers.
OL,18,F"BT Group continues to make
OL,19,Fsignificant investments in the rollout
OL,20,Fof full fibre broadband and 5G mobile
OL,21,Fconnectivity across Northern Ireland."
