OL,3,CFears for 300 jobs at BT call centre
OL,5,FThe economy minister said she has
OL,6,Fasked Invest NI to "ensure every step
OL,7,Fpossible is taken to support the staff
OL,8,Fimpacted".
OL,10,FShe said: "In line with his commitment
OL,11,Fto regional balance Conor Murphy met
OL,12,Fwith both CWU representatives and BT
OL,13,Fto retain these skilled jobs.
OL,15,F"He also supported Invest NI's
OL,16,Fconcerted efforts to work with BT to
OL,17,Ffind an alternative site within
OL,18,FEnniskillen so these jobs could be
OL,19,Fretained.
